metadata.description:
Airdropped items can be unlocked on https://bad-apes.com.

 Bad Ape NFT Club is a collection of 555 unique Bad Ape NFTs.

 BANC was airdropped as an event with the total trading volume of BAYC reaching 1,050,000 ETH on opensea. Airdropped items are locked and can be traded after unlocking.
